Qatar Islamic Bank
```

#### Source of Funds Clarification
```
Dear Customer,

Please provide supporting documentation explaining the source of funds for your recent transactions.

Reference Number: [CASE ID]
Required Document: Source of Funds Declaration
Deadline: [SLA DATE]

Thank you for your cooperation.
Qatar Islamic Bank
```

#### Employment Verification
```
Dear Customer,

Please provide an updated employment letter or proof of employment.

Reference Number: [CASE ID]
Required Document: Employment Letter
Deadline: [SLA DATE]

Thank you for your cooperation.
Qatar Islamic Bank
```

#### Income Documentation Request
```
Dear Customer,

Please submit documents supporting your declared income.

Reference Number: [CASE ID]
