## 37. EDD Completion Options & KYC Data Correction

### 37.1 Overview

When an EDD case is opened, the Business team must have multiple options to resolve the case based on the risk classification reason.

The system must NOT assume that every EDD case requires additional documentation from the customer.

**Available Resolution Options:**

| Option | Description | Use Case |
|--------|-------------|----------|
| Request Additional Documents | Request new documents from customer | Source of funds, income proof |
| Accept Current KYC | No additional documents needed | Risk due to nationality/occupation |
| Correct Customer Data | Update incorrect KYC information | Data entry errors, outdated info |
| Request Identity Verification | Selfie/Video/Branch verification | Identity confirmation needed |
| Escalate to Compliance | Transfer case for review | Complex or high-risk scenarios |

### 37.2 Request Additional Documents

In some cases, the bank may require additional documentation from the customer.

**Common Document Requests:**

