### 41.3 Customer Behavior Analysis

The system shall analyze the following behavioral indicators:

| Indicator | Weight | Description |
|-----------|--------|-------------|
| Previous KYC Compliance History | High | Track record of timely KYC updates |
| Document Submission Delays | High | Historical delays in submitting documents |
| Transaction Pattern Changes | Medium | Unusual transaction behavior |
| Contact Response Rate | Medium | Customer responsiveness to bank requests |
| Account Activity Level | Low | Active vs dormant account behavior |
| Risk Rating Changes | High | Historical risk rating movements |

