### 41.4 KYC Compliance Risk Score

The system shall generate a **KYC Compliance Risk Score** for each customer:

| Score Range | Risk Level | Action Required |
|-------------|------------|-----------------|
| 0-20 | Very Low | Standard monitoring |
| 21-40 | Low | Periodic review |
| 41-60 | Medium | Enhanced monitoring |
| 61-80 | High | Proactive outreach |
| 81-100 | Very High | Immediate action required |

**Score Calculation Formula:**

```
KYC_Risk_Score = 
  (Previous_Compliance_Weight × Previous_Compliance_Score) +
  (Document_Delay_Weight × Document_Delay_Score) +
  (Transaction_Pattern_Weight × Transaction_Pattern_Score) +
  (Contact_Response_Weight × Contact_Response_Score) +
  (Risk_Rating_Weight × Risk_Rating_Score)
```

---

