The system shall generate early warnings when:

| Trigger | Condition | Action |
|---------|-----------|--------|
| **High Risk Score** | KYC_Risk_Score > 60 | Alert RM and Operations |
| **Score Increase** | Score increased by >20 in 30 days | Review customer |
| **Approaching Expiry + High Risk** | KYC expires in 90 days AND Risk_Score > 50 | Proactive outreach |
| **Pattern Match** | Customer matches non-compliance pattern | Flag for review |
| **Multiple Red Flags** | 3+ behavioral indicators triggered | Escalate to Compliance |

